<span class="header1">TECHNOLOGY</span>
<p>If you like a hands-on approach to technology, you might like the occupations in this field.</p>

<hr size="1" />

	<span class="header2">Electronic Engineer</span><br /><br />
	<img class="job_pic" src="/images/icons/EF/C0936_02.jpg" width="100" height="100" border="0" alt="Electronic Engineer" />
	<span class="header3">Job Description</span>
	<blockquote>An electronic engineer helps to create things you use everyday such as radios, computers, and televsions.  In this job, you would design and test electronic equipment.  You might also oversee the making of this equipment.</blockquote>
	<span class="header3">Education</span>
	<blockquote>You need at least a Bachelor's Degree for this job.  Most employers are looking for people who have their Master's Degree or Ph.D.</blockquote>
	<span class="header3">Salary</span>
	<blockquote>The yearly salary ranges from $48,000 to $108,000 and would depend on the engineer's education and experience.</blockquote>

<hr size="1" />

	<span class="header2">Millwright</span><br /><br />
	<img class="job_pic" src="/images/icons/EF/C1610_07.jpg" width="100" height="100" border="0" alt="Millwright" />
	<span class="header3">Job Description</span>
	<blockquote>As a millwright, you would install, dismantle, and repair heavy machinery for any kind of industry. You would need to be able to read a blueprint.  This is a diagram that explains how the machine is constructed, and how it should be installed.  Millwrights use special tools, so you would also need to understand how tools work and use them correctly.</blockquote>
	<span class="header3">Education</span>
	<blockquote>You could become a millwright in two ways.  You might work as an apprentice to another millwright. An apprentice is someone who learns a trade by working on the job with an experienced person.  You might also attend a vocational tech program.</blockquote>
	<span class="header3">Salary</span>
	<blockquote>The yearly salary ranges from $26,000 to $65,000.</blockquote>

<hr size="1" />

	<span class="header2">Mechanical Engineering Technician</span><br /><br />
	<span class="header3">Job Description</span>
	<blockquote>A mechanical engineering technician helps an engineer to design equipment.  This might be industrial machinery and other equipment.  In this job, you would make sketches of machinery.  You would plan schedules.  You would also prepare layouts and estimate labor costs.  You would write reports too.</blockquote>
	<span class="header3">Education</span>
	<blockquote>Sometimes on-the-job training is available.  But most of the time, you need to have had previous training to get a job.  Vocational schools, community colleges, and the military offer this training.</blockquote>
	<span class="header3">Salary</span>
	<blockquote>The yearly salary ranges from $16,000 to $50,000.</blockquote>

